    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required Gradation levels at MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out per the ASME V&V 40-2018 credibility matrix for MRL 2 Class II devices. The Relevance of validation activities factor achieved Gradation 3, providing additional confidence beyond the minimum requirement. The CFD model is assessed as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met at all five evaluated operating points.",
